  <brief_title>Latanoprost for the Treatment of Menière's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel Group Study to Determine the Efficacy, the Duration of Action, and Safety of Latanoprost in Patients With Menière's Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Synphora AB</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Synphora AB</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the dose regimen, efficacy and safety of latanoprost
      for the treatment of Menière's disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
